<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>Implements<sp/>rigidbody<sp/>dynamics<sp/>with<sp/>force<sp/>and<sp/>torque<sp/>integration.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>Implements<sp/>force<sp/>generators<sp/>that<sp/>can<sp/>be<sp/>used<sp/>to<sp/>simulate<sp/>certain<sp/>forces<sp/>like<sp/>gravity,<sp/>drag,<sp/>buoyancy,<sp/>stiff<sp/>springs,<sp/>etc...</highlight></codeline>
